Text.string: Been waitin' for this, Vault Thief!

Oh, you WISH you had some of this!
Yeah, just TRY to stop me!
Let's get a little more intimate, shall we?
You can't run from me! Heh-heh!
Don't worry, Ty, I've got this!
Don't you see? You can't win!
Need some help from the fam!
The sky is falling, Vault Thief!
A little busy here, just piss off!
